OL,2,MSo - how does the Internet really work
OL,4,CJohanna
OL,5,CSun 12:40-13:10
OL,6,CStage B
OL,8,GLearn about the fascinating and fun
OL,9,Gworld of computer networks and the
OL,10,GInternet - with no previous knowledge
OL,11,Grequired. Have you ever wondered how
OL,12,Gthe Internet works? Or computer
OL,13,Gnetworks in general? Have you tried
OL,14,Glearning this in the past, but found
OL,15,Git too confusing or intimidating? Then
OL,16,Gthis talk might be for you. We will
OL,17,Gstart with a walkthrough of how data
OL,18,Gcrosses your home network. Building on
OL,19,Gthis, we will talk about how data
OL,20,Greaches your internet provider
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
